STEPS TO RUN:

Method 1: (Single/Batch Decode)

1. Run decode.sh to get necessary output in sample.out

2. Construct grammar file (JSGF) using my earlier scripts from phonemes2ngbphones

Method 2: (single phrase)

1. Use construct_grammar.py to construct different grammar using .phseg file using neighboring phones for each phone at a time and fixing all other phones

2. Create split.ctl file using extracted FSG_phrase/JSGF/

3. Run feature_extract.sh program to extract features for individual phoeme wav files

4. Java Speech Grammar Format (JSGF) files are already created in FSG_phoneme

5. Run jsgf2fsg.sh in FSG_3phoneme to convert from jsgf to fsg.

6. Run decode_phrase.py to decode to output_decoded_phrase.txt



